Package midiReference

Class Summary
MidiReference Collection of methods designed to make translating between the language of music to midi values.
 

Enum Summary
ChordReference Enum class providing access to ready made chord degrees based on scale references.
NoteReference Enum containing the basic note information at octave 0.
ScaleReference Enum class providing access to scales based on chromatic degree reference.
TimeBase Enumeration containing the number of pulses per rythm value (based on a 24PPQ MIDI sync clock)
